{"word":"G4895 - σύνειμι - sýneimi - soon'-i-mee - Be with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύνειμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sýneimi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon'-i-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to be with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a> (including its various inflections); to <i>be</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, <i>present</i> at the time: - be with.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}